        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[费解]#痛风的人到底能喝什么#？痛风患者要远离酒精！酒精既增加尿酸产生，又减少尿酸排泄，酒精摄入越多，痛风发作风险越大。其次，酒类都属于高嘌呤食物，尤其...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%97%9B%E9%A3%8E%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E8%83%BD%E5%96%9D%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%97%9B%E9%A3%8E%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E8%83%BD%E5%96%9D%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#痛风的人到底能喝什么#</span></a>？痛风患者要远离酒精！<br><br>酒精既增加尿酸产生，又减少尿酸排泄，酒精摄入越多，痛风发作风险越大。其次，酒类都属于高嘌呤食物，尤其是啤酒，其嘌呤含量非常高，白酒、红酒的嘌呤含量次之。因此，痛风患者应严格戒酒！<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>卫子建议，痛风患者日常应多饮水（每日饮水2升以上）、牛奶或乳制品，避免饮用可乐、橙汁等含糖软饮料，咖啡与高尿酸和痛风的关系目前尚无定论，可酌情饮用。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升v计划#</span></a>（健康中国）<img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjunmenn03j20j60jxgnt.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
